Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:23.08,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道被误解的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.75,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,(Missiles flying, children getting shot)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.75,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,（导弹凌空，孩童中弹）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:28.65,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Swindles everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:28.65,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是骗局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:33.40,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,People who should be the most loves ones, killing each other
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:33.40,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,原本至爱之人 如今互相屠戮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:40.20,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you keep an eye off, things get stolen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:40.20,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,一时松懈 万物尽失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:41.42,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,The world Is like this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:41.42,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:42.45,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,The world we don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:42.45,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:43.69,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,The unknown world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:43.69,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:47.11,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of our hands Covering it up, acting like you don't see a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:47.11,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,超出了我们的掌控 掩藏它吧，如同你从未目睹一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:50.25,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think it's a different thing You won't notice that the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:50.25,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,若你认为这只是不同的事情 你将不会发现 你所在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.76,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,you live in is eventually hitting towards this matter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.76,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,最终也会迎来这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:01:03.50,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at it Oh yeah ! The world is all linked together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:01:03.50,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,看着它！Oh Yeah！这世界已被链在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:06.46,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Save (hey!) our loved (hey!) ones and the world (because breaking)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:06.46,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,拯救所爱和这世界 （因为）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:10.11,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,(Down the pile wood castle is easy) The peaceful days lasting is a wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:10.11,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,（碾平圆木堆堡垒并非难事）持久的和平只是愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:12.66,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have no idea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:12.66,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:17.14,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,How many.. tickets "to live today" are.. (Left!!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:17.14,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,还剩多少“今日生还”的（入场券！）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:20.83,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Even at the time you were! playing cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:20.83,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,即便是你打扑克的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:26.58,OP_EN,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere in the world.. somebody is crying.. ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:26.58,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,这世界某处也有人正在号哭……Ah！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 宁子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.66,0:01:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 你忘记我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是女武神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:01:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有叫真子的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能不要用那个称呼我！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1107号 鹰鸟小鸟 到我这来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1107号是小鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 和我说的一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快夸夸我 千怜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1107号 我不允许你逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的生命是我的东西
